13:
Either way, give us the candy,
Or you're in for a TRICK tonight!
26: This isn't what I wanted to do...
30:
Come on, now. Keep your head up,
we're making record profits! We've
even got new sponsors lined up
from other worlds we've toured!
32:
What did you call it again? The Lil
Devil Dias? I'd say this new duo of
yours is working out quite well.
42:
Yeah, I kind of wanted to rebrand a
bit, change my image.
44:
It's basically impossible for me to do
so in my own world, after all. I just do
whatever I'm told to there...
47:
I feel like the exact same thing will
happen here, too, if things keep
going this way.
51:
You have to do whatever Regis tells
you?
55:
Well, not exactly. It's just... I don't
want to turn down offers for work,
you know?
57: A girl's gotta make a living, after all.
66:
Hmm. An ingenious idea has come
to me, my dear metallic maiden!
Come closer and I will tell you!
72: What kind of an idea?! Tell me!
75:
Hehehehe. Lend me an ear! Closer, I
say!
84: Whoa, really? No way? And then we—
87:
Perfect! Uh-huh, exactly! It's gonna
be so gooood...
102:
This area is looking great as well.
The spitting image of peace and
tranquility!
104:
Thanks to everyone's hard work, we
managed to dramatically reduce
peace-disturbing incidents in the
area—
106: The night is ours—as is your world!
117:
Even in the dead of night,
All eyes and electrons are on me!
119:
This is Diva Media, coming to
Palpebra with a special Halloween
performance!
124:
Featuring special guests from a
world away—the yokai!
129:
Come everyone, join us in song and
dance!
136:
W-wait a minute, what's going on
here?!
139:
Paranormal phenomena?
Monsters?! This is the doing of
someone from Alk's group of misfits,
no doubt!
144:
Hahaha! First she fraternizes with
humans, and now yokai...
146:
What am I ever to do with someone
as incorrigible as her?
153:
Hahahaha! Wooooow! That was so
much fun—we made such a ruckus!
156:
Did you SEE the looks on their faces?
We totally blew them out of the
water!
160:
Indeed! Our impromptu flash mob
concert idea was a smashing
success!
165: Did you have fun too, Stella?
170: Of course. It was a blast.
173:
Nice job, all of you! That was quite
the show—though I have to say, 
it was a bit on the noisy side.
177:
Hehe, we might have gone too far in
a few places!
181: Oh well, it's no big deal. Probably.
186:
Exactly, nothing to worry about!
Anyway, Dia... I gotta know—what's
our next target?!
189:
How about coming to MY world? We
could do a show on a BOAT! Ooh, or
we could commandeer a pirate ship!
195:
No, no, no. I must INSIST that for our
next show we visit Yamato! Let's host
a March of the Yokai, in celebration
of the newest edition of the Yokai
Encyclopedia!
200:
Huh? We've had more than enough
marching yokai!
204:
Ladies, ladies! Don't worry—we'll do it
ALL!
207:
You can bet your bottom credit that
I'm gonna keep singing everywhere I
can!
209:
Oh, this is so much fun... I can't
remember the last time I laughed
like this...
